{"tid":1602943,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"估唔到仲有人覺得可以跳過黑警，直面對準政權。","createTime":"2019-09-29T14:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T14:43:48.000Z","uid":34676,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"86a6b2aaa69cded380e3bc4f7e673a64072b44e8","tid":1602943,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:33:52.000Z","msg":"黑警冇事冇幹點解會同人民對立？<br />\n每日輕輕鬆鬆hea 下射下波又一日袋幾十k 唔好？<br />\n呢幾十k 係for 服務市民咩？<br />\n係for 服務港共啊<br />\n正正係因為佢地係政府爪牙<br />\n所以我哋先越唔過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日話要對準政權<br />\n你有邊一次活動想對準政權嘅時候黑警係唔會阻你啫？<br />\n呢個軍政府落嘅order 俾佢地可以無後果地犯法<br />\n佢地就正正係呢個腐敗嘅政權嘅一大部份啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28bdf8a3a0138baa656c3cb171b17705fb00d34","tid":1602943,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:34:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca6190843df845839f4a58b25b07945177d3785f","tid":1602943,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:35:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d666409706a1b306e252953f185b660dfc68c673","tid":1602943,"uid":311907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:36:19.000Z","msg":"內外同時做<br />\n<br />\n大家係咪唔記得好多野要繼續做？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602820</a>"},{"pid":"e977d3db613c1d8b3d39326519d86621df8a0f4e","tid":1602943,"uid":256142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:37:33.000Z","msg":"槍桿子裏面出政權<br />\n好似都係出自老毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f843758f1085c11c5ba78205c127b5da437e10","tid":1602943,"uid":3